      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Code verification benchmarks (patch tests, single-element tests) have been executed and documented for the element types used in the pedicle screw model. Results are within acceptable tolerances."
    },
    {
