      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "A systematic mesh convergence study was performed across three refinement levels. The quantity of interest (peak von Mises stress at screw-rod interface) changed by less than 2% between the two finest meshes, demonstrating discretization error is well controlled."
