      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Iterative solver convergence criteria were set to residual norms below 1e-6. Energy balance checks confirm solver errors are negligible relative to the quantities of interest."
