      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Model setup procedures are documented in a standard operating procedure. An independent analyst reviewed boundary conditions and material assignments against the test protocol. No use errors were identified."
