      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level; linear elastic continuum mechanics is appropriate for the load regime.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic continuum mechanics is justified for the sub-yield loading regime of the F1717 compression-bending test. Contact formulation at the screw-rod interface uses penalty-based frictionless contact, consistent with the lubricated test conditions."
