      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties (E=114 GPa, nu=0.34) are sourced from ASTM F136-13 certified coupon data provided by DePuy Synthes. Geometric inputs are derived from calibrated CMM measurements of the actual test articles."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
