      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level; quantitative comparison metric required.",
      "rationale": "Predicted construct stiffness and yield load were compared against experimental means using a normalized error metric. Mean absolute percentage error was 4.1% for stiffness and 5.8% for yield load across the N=11 constructs, satisfying the acceptance threshold of less than 10%."
    },
