      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level; validation scenario must be representative of the intended use scenario.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity replicates the F1717 test geometry, load configuration, and material system used in the regulatory submission. The validation scenario is judged to be representative of the submission-relevant use scenario, supporting the required relevance level."
