    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) was reviewed and accepted on the basis that the F1717 protocol specifies a single canonical load configuration and no regulatory precedent exists for multi-condition variation in this test type. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for the intended regulatory submission.",
